---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact — Freelancer Tax Estimator"
  description="Contact FreelancerTaxEstimator: report a bug, suggest a topic, request a correction to a tax figure, or get in touch with the editor."
>
  <article class="prose-content px-4 py-10">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p>
      The fastest way to reach the editor is by email:
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@freelancertaxestimator.com"
        ><strong>hello@freelancertaxestimator.com</strong></a
      >
    </p>

    <h2>What to send</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Errors in the calculator.</strong> Tell me which input you used,
        which output looked wrong, and what the IRS source says it should be.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Out-of-date figures.</strong> Include the IRS link to the
        current value.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Topics to cover.</strong> If you tried to look something up here
        and couldn't find it, that's a content gap I want to know about.
      </li>
      <li><strong>Press, partnerships, or sponsorship inquiries.</strong></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What I can't do</h2>
    <p>
      I can't review your specific tax situation or answer "what should I file"
      questions. For that, hire a CPA or Enrolled Agent — the IRS{" "}
      <a
        href="https://irs.treasury.gov/rpo/rpo.jsf"
        rel="noopener nofollow"
        target="_blank">tax preparer directory</a
      >{" "}
      is a starting point.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
      I read everything, but I can't always reply. Bug reports always get a
      response.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
